TextEng: I will listen. What is it you wish to say?
Text: 들을게. 무슨 말을 하고 싶은 거지?

TextEng: What do you want?
Speak, but waste my time and you'll regret it.
Text: 말해 봐라. 하지만 시간을 낭비하면 후회하게 될 거다.

TextEng: What you meaning? You please e'splain.
What you blather about, idiot?
Farewell for now.
Bye bye for nows.
I do what needs to be done. What is your offer?
Me does whatever. What you want?
Me nots evil!
I do not commit evil acts!
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> Me bad inside where good can't see!
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 겉으로는 안 보일 뿐, 속은 사악하지!

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> My evil is carefully veiled, making me more dangerous!
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 내 악의는 교묘히 감춰져 있지. 그래서 더 위험해!

TextEng: You wish me to bring them to you instead of Oleff?
You wants me to bring to you instead of Oleff?
Text: 올레프 말고 너한테 갖다 주라는 거야?

TextEng: Even in times of plague you scheme. How petty.
Even with plague around you act mean. Stupid.
Text: 역병 도는데도 못되게 굴어. 바보 같아.

TextEng: I will bring the artifacts to you instead of Oleff.
Me bring stuff to yous instead of Oleff stuffed-shirt.
Text: 폼만 잡는 올레프 대신 너한테 가져갈게.

TextEng: Why do you think I am working for Oleff?
Text: 왜 내가 올레프를 위해 일한다고 생각하지?

TextEng: Why you think me work for Oleff?
Text: 왜 내가 올레프 위해 일한다고 생각해?

TextEng: No! Me demands more!
The letter is unimportant. I don't need it.
Text: 그 편지는 중요하지 않아. 필요 없다.

TextEng: Letter dumb. Me not need.
Text: 편지 바보 같아. 나 필요 없어.

TextEng: Me not care about this.
Go over what is needed again.
Text: 필요한 걸 다시 한 번 정리해 줘.

TextEng: You repeat stuff about this job, okay?
Text: 이 일 다시 설명해 줘, 알았지?

TextEng: Farewell for now.
Bye bye for now.
Yeah yeah, I'll look into it sometime.
Me get around to it maybe later.
Go over the task with me. Perhaps I will help too.
Text: 의뢰 내용을 다시 설명해. 나도 도울지 모르니까.

TextEng: You tell me stuff too. Maybe me help.
Text: 너도 말해 봐. 나도 도울지 몰라.

TextEng: This doesn't interest me. Farewell.
Me not care much. Bye.
Text: 나 별로 신경 안 써. 잘 있어.

TextEng: Me gots stuff from one of the tomb-things.
Text: 나 저 무덤들 중 하나에서 물건 가져왔어.

TextEng: I have an artifact from one of the tombs.
I have no interest in this.
<StartAction>Describe the recovery of the Ancient Chronicles of Never.</Start>
<StartAction>Describe the recovery of Halueth Never's rusted armor.</Start>
Text: <StartAction>할루스 네버의 녹슨 갑옷을 회수한 경위를 설명합니다.</Start>

TextEng: Nevermind.
<StartAction>Describe the recovery of the Ancient Holy Symbol of Tyr.</Start>
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> You must agree that I am worth more.
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 내 값어치가 더 하다는 데 동의하겠지.

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> You knows me worth more than that.
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 나 그보다 값어치 더 있는 거 알잖아.

TextEng: I demand more! Appease me or die!
Text: 더 내놔! 내놓지 않으면 죽게 될 거다!

TextEng: Me get more or you die like dog!
Me come back if find more, okay.
That is sufficient. Thank you.
That really good. Thanks for the stuff.
I shall return if I find more.
That will not do! I demand more!
You were at the tomb and didn't help the dying?
Text: 무덤에 있었으면서, 죽어 가는 사람을 돕지 않았다고?

TextEng: You was there and didn't help the dying guys?
Text: 거기 있었으면서 죽어 가는 사람들 안 도왔다고?

TextEng: That's despicable! Give me Jacob's quill NOW!
You evil dumb-head! Give me Jacob's write-y thing NOW!
Text: 악독한 놈! 제이콥의 쓰는 거 당장 내놔!

TextEng: Give me the Quill now, you evil bastard!
Text: 깃펜을 지금 당장 내놔, 이 악당아!

TextEng: You gives me Quill right now, jerk!
Text: 지금 당장 깃펜 내놔, 이 자식아!

TextEng: What are the tenets of your faith in Talona?
What Talona? What she stand for?
How you knows about artifact stuff to start?
Text: 너 처음에 유물 같은 거 어떻게 알았어?

TextEng: How did you know of the artifacts to begin with?
You was there and didn't help the dying guys?
Text: 너 거기 있었는데 죽어가는 사람들 안 도와줬어?

TextEng: You were there and didn't help the dying?
Text: 거기 있었으면서 죽어가는 사람들을 안 도와준 거야?

TextEng: You evil dumb-head! Give me Jacob's write-y thing NOW!
Text: 너 나쁜 멍청이! 제이콥의 깃펜 당장 내놔!

TextEng: That's despicable! Give me Jacob's quill NOW!
Text: 정말 비열하군! 제이콥의 깃펜 당장 내놔!
